<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="History of Petrykivka Painting"
      description="The history of Petrykivka painting from its 18th-century origins to the present: chepurushky, Tetyana Pata, Oleksandr Statyva, the Petrykivka School, the Druzhba factory, Vasyl Sokolenko, UNESCO recognition, and the craft's state today."
